pzbmt@tue.nl.=20
=A0=A0=20
The application should consist of the following parts:=20
=A0=20
=A0=A0=A0=A0 * a detailed curriculum vitae;=20
=A0=A0=A0=A0 * an explanation of your interest in the proposed=20
research field;=20
=A0=A0=A0=A0 * a complete list of the courses you have attended=20
and corresponding grades, name of at least two references,=20
and all other information that might be relevant to your=20
application;=20
=A0=A0=A0=A0 * proof of English language skills (if applicable).=20
=A0=20
(Please mention the vacancy number V50.122 in the=20
subject.)=A0=20
=A0=A0=20
